<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[ن]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[اليَقَن]</span>: اليقين.<span class="c5"> يقال:</span> نحن على يَقَنٍ من ذلك.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
